reviews.text:
Stopped in on my way home from airport after being out of town for a few days;
Was craving pizza; so I choose HOT BOX;
Great decision! Front counter guy was friendly and very professional, also he suggested a few options to me and explained them very well...
Ended up choosing the 10" Ballsagna and salad;
And bam, it hit the spot; 
I ate at store; place was steadily busy with carryout and a few that dined in...
The help once again was very prompt with everyone that I could hear/see.
(I was seated close to counter)
After finishing up had to get a take out order for later tonight; was full but knew I'd still be craving more;
And another plus; the kitchen from counter looked very well maintained, dining floor and tables were clean and bathroom also... Those things make a great place even better, putting them over the top...
I only post if I feel like a place really is subpar and needs to be brought to attention or if I had a very awesome experience....
This one obviously was over the top!!!
I've ate at other HOT BOX pizzas and I liked them all but this place took the cake... I mean pie..
Thanks BROWNSBURG HOT BOX for a great welcoming home experience!!!!
